\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Nebuchadnezzar. This one built the Temple, and that one destroyed it. This one reigned forty years, 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ and that one reigned forty years. \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ he who swears\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  This is Zedekiah, who swore falsely, as it is said (II 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Chron. 36:13): “And he also rebelled against King Nebuchadnezzar, who adjured him, etc.” \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ like him 
